## Description
This is an effects processor for the currently titled fx-thing I am working on. It is (will eventually be) a node based audio effect processing engine meant to run on a standalone device, but is currently meant to use USB audio interfaces for physical interface through JACK.

## Dependencies
```
cmake
ninja
clang
jack2
```

## Building
Initialize build files
`cmake -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug`
Build
`cmake --build build`

## Running
`./build/cpp-fxprocessor